<a href="https://www.iono.fm/e/779248">Content hosted by iono.fm</a> Global real estate remains an attractive asset class for South African investors wanting to add offshore and asset class diversification to their portfolios. The story of Orbvest, involving some local business personalities that have set up a real estate investment company helping investors from South Africa mainly, invest in their very focussed Medical Real Estate category, is interesting for a number of reasons and Classic Business Anchor Michael Avery sits down with Martin Freeman, the New York-based SA-born CEO of OrbVest, to find out how the model works. This interview was originally broadcast on the Classic Business show with Michael Avery. Brought to you by OrbVest.